{"author":"Sunan Ibn Majah","hadith":{"hadithnumber":1296,"arabicnumber":1296,"text":"। আলী (রাঃ) থেকে বর্ণিত। তিনি বলেন, পায়ে হেঁটে ঈদগাহে যাওয়া সুন্নাতের অন্তর্ভুক্ত।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan Lighairihi"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":5,"hadith":494}}}